title: Ep 24: Manifesting and Makeup feat. Kelli Anne
itunes:title: Ep 24: Manifesting and Makeup feat. Kelli Anne
description: Shannon sits down with celebrity makeup artist and friend Kelli Anne to discuss a little bit of makeup, and a whole lot of everything else. How to navigate rejections and how to parlay them into following your passions, Kelli tells us about manifesting her life as an independent full time makeup artist in NYC. Shannon spills her best spray tan secrets, and tells us one of her big goals for the future. Does Oracle spray for roaches or hire life coaches? Shannon doesn’t know. What’s one of the girls biggest icks? Listen to Season 2 Episode 10 of Probably a Podcast to find out.
